notifyActivation

protected void notifyActivation(org.xml.sax.Attributes atts)
Description copied from class: DynamicContentHandlerBase
Called by setReader to forward the attributes to the new content handler specializt. This is a hook one can use to only handle attributes and still leave the handling of the setReader responsibilities to this base class.
